      "author": "joelwongjy",
      "description": "First release of **Bible Verse Tips**.\n\n- Hover (desktop) or tap (mobile) any Bible reference to preview the verse, in Reading view and Live Preview.\n- Click a reference to open the whole chapter in a built-in reader with chapter navigation.\n- Inline translation switcher: NIV, NLT, ESV, NKJV, NASB, AMP, MSG, NET, KJV, WEB and many more.\n\n### Manual install\nCopy `main.js`, `manifest.json` and `styles.css` into\n`<vault>/.obsidian/plugins/bible-verse-tips/`, then enable the plugin in\nSettings → Community plugins.",
